STATE of North Carolina
v.
Shane EVILSIZER No. 181P19 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 11, 2019 Shane Evilsizer, for Evilsizer, Shane. Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, William R. West, District Attorney, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 15th of May 2019 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Cumberland County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 11th of June 2019."
